Module it.polimi.ingsw.gc27
Package it.polimi.ingsw.gc27.View

Interface View

All Known Implementing Classes:
Gui, Tui
public interface View
The View interface represents the collection of methods for displaying and interacting with game-related information. Implementing classes are expected to provide methods to display various aspects of the game state and handle user interactions. Different implementations of the View interface can be used to provide different user interfaces, such as a command line interface or a graphical user interface.
